{"tid":1297852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（人唔到，禮都要到）陳茂波：將努力在法律上拆牆鬆綁 推動大灣區融合工作","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T08:07:20.000Z","uid":264683,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55ce4a88171eec76de801ee3735a24a86fae7f84","tid":1297852,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"財政司長陳茂波出席一論壇言表示，香港未來的金融發展應專注在，服務實體經濟、促進國家資本市場發展及推動大灣區金融合作。他認為，在大灣區政策下，香港將努力在法律上拆牆鬆綁，為兩地資產管理業界拓闊銷售渠道及營造有利的稅務環境。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n另外，他亦認為在促進國家資本市場發展上，香港應研究如何利用滬港通、深港通及債券通，擴大可交易的金融產品種類，促進兩地市場互聯互通。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n而在服務實體經濟方面，主要是發揮香港的國際財資中心與離岸人民幣中心的角色，協助內地企業融資。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/20763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F20763&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=199aa674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/20763</a><br />\n<br />\n政府點解唔回應77事變呀<br />\n答案就係研究緊仲有咩途徑可以繼續送中囉，成個大灣區計劃根本就係最大賣港缺口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個奴才都賣港賣唔切<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>送人不成就送地送錢</strong></span>，我呸<br />\n正式人唔到，禮(錢)都要到<br />\n<br />\n希望大家救完義士，可以考慮下針對呢個濕鳩大灣區計劃作出示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4729919d727c7a4420e44da13606fa1e3b1118b1","tid":1297852,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2d9737ffa68cbbb26005afad91348698ce76191d","tid":1297852,"uid":12824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a39c413ba092e60068b21b2cc930fe15d3003d7","tid":1297852,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12057df35a2a3d12cc32f93cfbec58f21233800c","tid":1297852,"uid":258120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌！俾我地抖下得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0959392c7a04208511309cff549628cc141bbee0","tid":1297852,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:02.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619fb486bbbcd3c792aa4ad844a967e7d2a77d47","tid":1297852,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dde5cbc125f0ac34ad12b26cecad6c836c03d062","tid":1297852,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:39:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2682e1cf622ae828728385e8b0f3541d3a8eac01","tid":1297852,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"個正苦真係759 日日不停撥火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ef77547767481ec50811ca3fa1d3e07f847f58","tid":1297852,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ce4a88171eec76de801ee3735a24a86fae7f84","tid":1297852,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"財政司長陳茂波出席一論壇言表示，香港未來的金融發展應專注在，服務實體經濟、促進國家資本市場發展及推動大灣區金融合作。他認為，在大灣區政策下，香港將努力在法律上拆牆鬆綁，為兩地資產管理業界拓闊銷售渠道及營造有利的稅務環境。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n另外，他亦認為在促進國家資本市場發展上，香港應研究如何利用滬港通、深港通及債券通，擴大可交易的金融產品種類，促進兩地市場互聯互通。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n而在服務實體經濟方面，主要是發揮香港的國際財資中心與離岸人民幣中心的角色，協助內地企業融資。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/20763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F20763&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=199aa674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/20763</a><br />\n<br />\n政府點解唔回應77事變呀<br />\n答案就係研究緊仲有咩途徑可以繼續送中囉，成個大灣區計劃根本就係最大賣港缺口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個奴才都賣港賣唔切<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>送人不成就送地送錢<